I said, "Hey, you guys;

00:20:34.710 --> 00:20:36.010
the better you are at math,

00:20:36.010 --> 00:20:39.100
the less likely you
are to get ripped off."

00:20:39.100 --> 00:20:41.660
And by the way, how many of you
guys want to start a business?

00:20:41.660 --> 00:20:42.960
Ever thought of starting
your own business?"

00:20:42.960 --> 00:20:44.280
Math-- you have?

00:20:44.280 --> 00:20:46.660
Oh yeah; okay, well how many
of you guys ever thought

00:20:46.660 --> 00:20:47.960
of starting your own business?

00:20:47.960 --> 00:20:49.540
Yeah, you have?

00:20:49.540 --> 00:20:50.840
Yeah, it's great.

00:20:50.840 --> 00:20:52.140
Owning your own business
is empowering;

00:20:52.140 --> 00:20:53.630
you're not working
for somebody else.

00:20:53.630 --> 00:20:54.930
But guess what?

00:20:54.930 --> 00:20:57.200
Guess what's going to
keep the doors open?

00:20:57.200 --> 00:20:58.560
Math. Yes.

00:20:58.560 --> 00:21:01.010
Because there are a lot
of really talented people

00:21:01.010 --> 00:21:03.910
out there, who are artists
or they have great ideas

00:21:03.910 --> 00:21:06.000
for businesses, but guess what?

00:21:06.000 --> 00:21:07.830
They don't know how to
manage their own money.

00:21:07.830 --> 00:21:10.890
Why? Maybe because they're--
they avoided math as a child.

00:21:10.890 --> 00:21:13.090
And if you're afraid of math
as a child, you're going

00:21:13.090 --> 00:21:14.790
to avoid numbers as an adult.

00:21:14.790 --> 00:21:16.090
You're just going to avoid them.

00:21:16.090 --> 00:21:17.970
And that gets you in trouble.

