&gt;&gt; What was the hardest
type of math?

00:25:44.250 --> 00:25:45.550
&gt;&gt; Danica McKellar: The
hardest type of math

00:25:45.550 --> 00:25:51.500
that I ever took was probably
real analysis, in college,

00:25:51.500 --> 00:25:54.510
where you prove the theorems
that you, the calculus theorems

00:25:54.510 --> 00:25:56.810
that you learn in
