00:25:58.920 --> 00:26:03.060
But part of why I liked math is
because it was so challenging.

00:26:03.060 --> 00:26:05.110
Because I was like, "Oh,
there's no way I'm going

00:26:05.110 --> 00:26:07.890
to be able to do this."

00:26:07.890 --> 00:26:11.180
And I'd, "Oh, that
sounds like a challenge.

00:26:11.180 --> 00:26:13.230
I wonder if I-- oh, I can."

00:26:13.230 --> 00:26:18.980
This is-- I approach a
lot of life like this.

