enjoy challenges.

00:27:22.610 --> 00:27:24.520
Learn to enjoy challenges.

00:27:24.520 --> 00:27:29.210
Learn to embrace them
because they're going

00:27:29.210 --> 00:27:34.420
to keep happening your entire
life, in all categories of life.

